<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/7977> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #7977" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/5> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Leg., lieut. 36. In MRR 2.405, refer also to ILLRP 426, and on his status as pr. desig. To Dio 48.36.4.[159]\n" .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/6390> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #6390" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Legatus pro praetore (ILS 8891). Held command for Pompey of western Sicily against Lepidus (App. BC 5.97- 98). Summoned to Messana after Naulochus, and surrendered when Pompey fled to the East (App. BC 5.122)." .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/10497> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #10497" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/21> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "MRR (citing ILLRP 426=ILS 8891) has Plinius as legatus pro praetore & praetor designatus. If legatus in 36, perhaps designated praetor for the following year" .
